{"tid":1899740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"願榮光歸香港","createTime":"2020-02-26T19:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T20:44:43.000Z","uid":167441,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b026345acef27a0b632851c74bdf70154c593fe7","tid":1899740,"uid":167441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T19:39:51.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得國歌點唱？ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoUIDL4SB60g%26feature%3Dshare&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplAqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=94236ce4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g&amp;feature=share</a><br />\n<br />\n記唔記得個陣個個星期都唱 <br />\n記唔記我我地有幾高昂士氣 <br />\n記唔記得每次唱個陣都眼濕濕 <br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得個感覺 <br />\n<br />\n依家諗返起 記住佢 <br />\n<br />\n商場唱唔到 可唔可以屋企唱 <br />\n <br />\n10點鐘可唔可以對住個窗唱？ <br />\n<br />\n由六月開始 <br />\n香港人一次又一次創造奇蹟<br />\n可唔可以一齊10點唱 <br />\n記返起個感覺 <br />\n<br />\n繼續抗爭落去 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽晚 10點一齊唱國歌  嗌口號 </span></span>"},{"pid":"67f96ae17ef566d5810ca2d3e085ce6d1ca2ed3c","tid":1899740,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T20:39:05.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"58bfe597fc5cbe9e3e36fe787a9bdca3ee8a3e6d","tid":1899740,"uid":167441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67f96ae17ef566d5810ca2d3e085ce6d1ca2ed3c","tid":1899740,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T20:39:05.000Z","msg":"唉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T20:40:18.000Z","msg":"可以氣餒但唔可以放棄<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"db0e254b120832247bcf126529e0f248285b629c","tid":1899740,"uid":350660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T20:44:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}